(150332, '{"citation":"Reprise de confiance en soi par le sport\\n","phenomenal":"Participations aux \\u00e9v\\u00e9nements FFH, s\\u00e9ances d''initiations.","quisuisje":"comite","partners":"DDCS, service droits des femmes","participants":"50"}'),
